  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ta-daah!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424240/extras/f5694fac7a51429451a96be844116692.avif?t=1774274892\" width=240 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm Cygnus, the Great Sage living at the edge of the forest!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, the demon lord suddenly appeared in the peaceful kingdom of Corvus!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424240/extras/74f05fd58ec2bffb8bcd056da2627e66.avif?t=1774274892\" width=240 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The king and everyone else in the kingdom have all perished! What should we do!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ah! There's Sir Lyra!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Isn't that Sir Lyra, the loyal knight of the kingdom?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's defeat the demon lord together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I have a secret weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's called the...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424240/extras/314cce072bd4341c9e12afc90ff70ad1.avif?t=1774274892\" width=640 height=480 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Pudding: Lyre Knight</i> is the 13th title in the Katatema series, a unique and thrilling action-adventure of destruction!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Minimal buttons! A simple control scheme.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Deal with terrifying attacks easily using tools like the Happiness Ring!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Designed to be fun and easy to play, even for those not skilled in shooting games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Collect items as you play and admire them in the collection room.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* A gradually unfolding world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* A reliable companion always by your side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* The music is all new tracks by Watson, and the soundtrack is also available.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're welcome to stream this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please avoid major spoilers in the thumbnails.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ta-daah!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424240/extras/f5694fac7a51429451a96be844116692.avif?t=1774274892\" width=240 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm Cygnus, the Great Sage living at the edge of the forest!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, the demon lord suddenly appeared in the peaceful kingdom of Corvus!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424240/extras/74f05fd58ec2bffb8bcd056da2627e66.avif?t=1774274892\" width=240 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The king and everyone else in the kingdom have all perished! What should we do!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ah! There's Sir Lyra!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Isn't that Sir Lyra, the loyal knight of the kingdom?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's defeat the demon lord together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I have a secret weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's called the...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424240/extras/314cce072bd4341c9e12afc90ff70ad1.avif?t=1774274892\" width=640 height=480 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Pudding: Lyre Knight</i> is the 13th title in the Katatema series, a unique and thrilling action-adventure of destruction!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Minimal buttons! A simple control scheme.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Deal with terrifying attacks easily using tools like the Happiness Ring!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Designed to be fun and easy to play, even for those not skilled in shooting games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Collect items as you play and admire them in the collection room.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* A gradually unfolding world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* A reliable companion always by your side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* The music is all new tracks by Watson, and the soundtrack is also available.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're welcome to stream this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please avoid major spoilers in the thumbnails.</p>",
